<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='615000' id='t-615000'>And that's the process we took -- let me show you how the engine works.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='618000' id='t-618000'>The simplest heat engine, or hot air engine, of all time</span>
