<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='673000' id='t-673000'>And then Robert Stirling came along with this genius idea,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='675000' id='t-675000'>which was, well I'm still not heating the metal now,</span>
