<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='727000' id='t-727000'>So we really set out on a path to try and make the lowest cost possible.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='731000' id='t-731000'>We built a huge mathematical model of how a Stirling engine works.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='733000' id='t-733000'>We applied the genetic algorithm.</span>
